{"tid":2348803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日媒指至少44名日籍科研人員參與中國「千人計劃」","createTime":"2021-01-01T04:58:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T07:04:24.000Z","uid":333,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e409916a0f492584f6b7e772fd2c7e20185fb9bc","tid":2348803,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T04:58:49.000Z","msg":"日媒指至少44名日籍科研人員參與中國「千人計劃」<br />\n<br />\n日本傳媒報道，至少有44名日籍研究人員參與中國招攬人才的「千人計劃」，日本政府為防止關鍵經濟與安保技術外流，檢討加強規管。《讀賣新聞》報道，參與「千人計劃」的日籍研究人員中，部分人從日本政府領取高額研究經費後，再前往與中國軍隊有關的大學研究。日本政府將要求接受政府資金的研究人員，公開海外相關活動。報道指出，其中13人過去10年獲得日本政府資助，總研究經費約45億日圓。"},{"pid":"7af069b233f29927173ed3012c55953ab5673a96","tid":2348803,"uid":263534,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T05:01:57.000Z","msg":"遲醒好過唔識醒"},{"pid":"fd5b414a376b91a7b11b03f410d132de28eec442","tid":2348803,"uid":333,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T05:03:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.yomiuri.co.jp/politics/20201231-OYT1T50192/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yomiuri.co.jp%2Fpolitics%2F20201231-OYT1T50192%2F&d=h8K6dYNnEA4rSgnLcindhXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=e01045b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.yomiuri.co.jp/politics/20201231-OYT1T50192/</a><br />\n<br />\n讀賣新聞嘅原文報導"},{"pid":"533ef99049f7fefae0b9a362a47766b4ac7f15b0","tid":2348803,"uid":51583,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T05:03:23.000Z","msg":"全世界都搵晒呢D人出黎已經幫到好多"},{"pid":"4b7a385d2636d7f0018469d26a50e8e9163328ab","tid":2348803,"uid":355748,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T05:05:20.000Z","msg":"唔掃清啲無間道開唔到戰"},{"pid":"bf081d5677dfab8c3f0c67d70540d8df2503df31","tid":2348803,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T05:08:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28eb93ca694e314c67113c4dfee6f4987daf2093","tid":2348803,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T05:08:58.000Z","msg":"死